Package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo.bitcore

package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo.bitcore
Objects for BitCore indexing as implemented in OmniCore.

Requires running OmniCore with -experimental-btc-balances=1

See Also:
  • Data retrieval (address index) in OmniCore RPC API

    OmniCore PR #1180
